Rating: 3
I am not one to skimp on sugar or butter in a dessert but was making this for people who will not eat full fat desserts and came up with wonderful results by reducing a few ingredients. Reduce butter to 3T in crust (I also add a pinch of salt), cream cheese to 5oz, peanut butter to 1/2 cup and sugar to 1/3 cup. I've made this before following the exact recipe and the lower fat version is even better than the original.

